     SHORT="ksubeditor creates and edits subtitles for DivX movies."
      LONG="
ksubeditor is a DivX subtitle editor for KDE 3.x.
It is able to edit and convert subtitles between 
different subtitle formats.
It is able to easily change the time of 
the subtitle and fit it to the movie.
